{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":746,"text":"I've been intrigued by this question"},{"time":2931,"text":"of whether we could evolve\nor develop a sixth sense --"},{"time":7382,"text":"a sense that would give us seamless access"},{"time":11000,"text":"and easy access to meta-information\nor information that may exist somewhere"},{"time":17000,"text":"that may be relevant to help us\nmake the right decision"},{"time":20000,"text":"about whatever it is\nthat we're coming across."},{"time":23864,"text":"And some of you may argue,"},{"time":26000,"text":"\"Well, don't today's cell phones\ndo that already?\""},{"time":29286,"text":"But I would say no."},{"time":31000,"text":"When you meet someone here at TED --"},{"time":33000,"text":"and this is the top networking place,\nof course, of the year --"},{"time":37063,"text":"you don't shake somebody's hand"},{"time":38945,"text":"and then say,\n\"Can you hold on for a moment"},{"time":41000,"text":"while I take out my phone and Google you?\""},{"time":44110,"text":"Or when you go to the supermarket"},{"time":47000,"text":"and you're standing there\nin that huge aisle"},{"time":49833,"text":"of different types of toilet papers,"},{"time":52373,"text":"you don't take out your cell phone,\nand open a browser,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and go to a website to try to decide\nwhich of these different toilet papers"},{"time":61000,"text":"is the most ecologically\nresponsible purchase to make."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65084,"text":"So we don't really have easy access\nto all this relevant information"},{"time":69000,"text":"that can just help us\nmake optimal decisions"},{"time":72994,"text":"about what to do next\nand what actions to take."},{"time":76171,"text":"And so my research group at the Media Lab"},{"time":79000,"text":"has been developing a series of inventions"},{"time":83884,"text":"to give us access to this information\nin a sort of easy way,"},{"time":88485,"text":"without requiring that the user\nchanges any of their behavior."},{"time":93481,"text":"And I'm here to unveil our latest effort,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and most successful effort so far,"},{"time":100000,"text":"which is still very much\na work in process."},{"time":102834,"text":"I'm actually wearing the device right now\nand we've sort of cobbled it together"},{"time":108000,"text":"with components that are off the shelf --"},{"time":111682,"text":"and that, by the way, only cost\n350 dollars at this point in time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116602,"text":"I'm wearing a camera,\njust a simple web cam,"},{"time":120582,"text":"a portable, battery-powered\nprojection system with a little mirror."},{"time":126354,"text":"These components communicate\nto my cell phone in my pocket"},{"time":130449,"text":"which acts as the communication\nand computation device."},{"time":134754,"text":"And in the video here we see\nmy student Pranav Mistry,"},{"time":138698,"text":"who's really the genius\nwho's been implementing"},{"time":141000,"text":"and designing this whole system."},{"time":143391,"text":"And we see how this system\nlets him walk up to any surface"},{"time":149000,"text":"and start using his hands\nto interact with the information"},{"time":153000,"text":"that is projected in front of him."},{"time":155716,"text":"The system tracks\nthe four significant fingers."},{"time":159838,"text":"In this case, he's wearing\nsimple marker caps"},{"time":163528,"text":"that you may recognize."},{"time":165000,"text":"But if you want a more stylish version,"},{"time":167714,"text":"you could also paint your nails\nin different colors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171415,"text":"And the camera basically\ntracks these four fingers"},{"time":175000,"text":"and recognizes any gestures\nthat he's making"},{"time":178863,"text":"so he can just go to,\nfor example, a map of Long Beach,"},{"time":183389,"text":"zoom in and out, etc."},{"time":185651,"text":"The system also recognizes iconic gestures\nsuch as the \"take a picture\" gesture,"},{"time":191769,"text":"and then takes a picture\nof whatever is in front of you."},{"time":195211,"text":"And when he then walks\nback to the Media Lab,"},{"time":198000,"text":"he can just go up to any wall"},{"time":200469,"text":"and project all the pictures\nthat he's taken,"},{"time":203405,"text":"sort through them and organize them,\nand re-size them, etc.,"},{"time":207000,"text":"again using all natural gestures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210848,"text":"So, some of you most likely\nwere here two years ago"},{"time":214931,"text":"and saw the demo by Jeff Han,\nor some of you may think,"},{"time":219209,"text":"\"Well, doesn't this look like\nthe Microsoft Surface Table?\""},{"time":222604,"text":"And yes, you also interact\nusing natural gestures,"},{"time":227000,"text":"both hands, etc."},{"time":229000,"text":"But the difference here\nis that you can use any surface,"},{"time":232000,"text":"you can walk up to any surface,"},{"time":235000,"text":"including your hand,\nif nothing else is available,"},{"time":238000,"text":"and interact with this projected data."},{"time":241521,"text":"The device is completely\nportable, and can be --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251568,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253405,"text":"So, one important difference\nis that it's totally mobile."},{"time":257000,"text":"Another even more important\ndifference is that in mass production,"},{"time":261758,"text":"this would not cost more tomorrow\nthan today's cell phones"},{"time":265447,"text":"and would actually not\nsort of be a bigger packaging --"},{"time":269449,"text":"could look a lot more stylish"},{"time":271495,"text":"than this version\nthat I'm wearing around my neck."},{"time":276133,"text":"But other than letting some of you\nlive out your fantasy"},{"time":280903,"text":"of looking as cool as Tom Cruise\nin \"Minority Report,\""},{"time":284858,"text":"the reason why we're really\nexcited about this device"},{"time":288900,"text":"is that it really can act\nas one of these sixth-sense devices"},{"time":294756,"text":"that gives you relevant information\nabout whatever is in front of you."},{"time":300032,"text":"So we see Pranav here\ngoing into the supermarket"},{"time":304000,"text":"and he's shopping for some paper towels."},{"time":307364,"text":"And, as he picks up a product,"},{"time":309292,"text":"the system can recognize\nthe product that he's picking up,"},{"time":312370,"text":"using either image recognition\nor marker technology,"},{"time":316630,"text":"and give him the green light\nor an orange light."},{"time":319628,"text":"He can ask for additional information."},{"time":322562,"text":"So this particular choice here"},{"time":326347,"text":"is a particularly good choice,\ngiven his personal criteria."},{"time":330000,"text":"Some of you may want the toilet paper\nwith the most bleach in it"},{"time":334000,"text":"rather than the most ecologically\nresponsible choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337595,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":340772,"text":"If he picks up a book in the bookstore,\nhe can get an Amazon rating --"},{"time":345504,"text":"it gets projected\nright on the cover of the book."},{"time":348140,"text":"This is Juan's book, our previous speaker,"},{"time":352000,"text":"which gets a great rating,\nby the way, at Amazon."},{"time":354732,"text":"And so, Pranav turns the page of the book"},{"time":357000,"text":"and can then see additional\ninformation about the book --"},{"time":360756,"text":"reader comments, maybe sort of information\nby his favorite critic, etc."},{"time":367000,"text":"If he turns to a particular page,"},{"time":369000,"text":"he finds an annotation by maybe\nan expert or a friend of ours"},{"time":373317,"text":"that gives him a little bit\nof additional information"},{"time":376163,"text":"about whatever is on that particular page."},{"time":379212,"text":"Reading the newspaper --\nit never has to be outdated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383613,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"You can get video annotations\nof the events that you're reading about."},{"time":389813,"text":"You can get the latest sports scores, etc."},{"time":393884,"text":"This is a more controversial one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397675,"text":"As you interact with someone at TED,"},{"time":400000,"text":"maybe you can see\na word cloud of the tags,"},{"time":404000,"text":"the words that are associated\nwith that person"},{"time":406752,"text":"in their blog and personal web pages."},{"time":409524,"text":"In this case, the student\nis interested in cameras, etc."},{"time":414701,"text":"On your way to the airport,"},{"time":416681,"text":"if you pick up your boarding pass, it can\ntell you that your flight is delayed,"},{"time":420774,"text":"that the gate has changed, etc."},{"time":423434,"text":"And, if you need to know\nwhat the current time is,"},{"time":426578,"text":"it's as simple as drawing a watch --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431229,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":432388,"text":"on your arm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435614,"text":"So that's where we're at so far\nin developing this sixth sense"},{"time":442000,"text":"that would give us seamless access\nto all this relevant information"},{"time":446750,"text":"about the things that we may come across."},{"time":449592,"text":"My student Pranav, who's really,\nlike I said, the genius behind this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454010,"text":"(Applause and cheering)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":474845,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":476000,"text":"He does deserve a lot of applause,"},{"time":479000,"text":"because I don't think he's slept much\nin the last three months, actually."},{"time":483372,"text":"And his girlfriend is probably\nnot very happy about him either."},{"time":486798,"text":"But it's not perfect yet,\nit's very much a work in progress."},{"time":491677,"text":"And who knows, maybe in another 10 years"},{"time":494634,"text":"we'll be here with the ultimate\nsixth sense brain implant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500071,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}